{
  "stem": "43.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she-- so she told me, oh, you Sonia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I tell her maybe-- maybe you saw my-- my-- somebody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She know my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She knows my sister.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- we can talk here nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Come with me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She took my hand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She helped me to get up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she took me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She told me that yesterday came two men to the-- to the town, to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "From there into Ukraine killed her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If you were [INAUDIBLE] they will kill you too because they want-- they took everything away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They don't want [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she told me [INAUDIBLE] I was going [? with her. ?] So she-- she tell me, I have so much to tell you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Come with me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have to tell you-- to tell you something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So dear sister, what-- what she was saying-- so when the-- when the year the [INAUDIBLE] tomorrow the ghetto, they'll be every killed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she came the night to the-- to [INAUDIBLE] to the Ukraine camp and told me, I will give you up everything I have over there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's a grave, and I have everything over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will give you up everything and take me with.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she got all three children also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She's the only-- before me, the sister there was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she takes me by my hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She show me outside by [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a little place what is a little [? cave ?] around and around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All right?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] your sister with the three children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now you have everything she brought to me, I want to give you up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I told her, no, my dear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would like to help my sister or her child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Things I don't know where to go, and I don't need nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
